            <title>[SOLR-497] SolrJ QueryResponse does not support date faceting results</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-497</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The QueryResponse provides getFacetFields for drilling down into facets.  It would also be handy to have similar info for facet dates.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
